## seed: The seed for the PRNG.
##
## .. bro:see:: rand
##
## .. note::
##
##      This function is a wrapper about the function ``srandom``
##      provided by the OS.
function srand%(seed: count%): any
	%{
	bro_srandom(seed);
	return 0;
	%}

